---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">
      About AssureGuard Insurance Services
    </h1>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 p-4">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          At AssureGuard Insurance Services, our mission is to provide
          comprehensive and reliable insurance solutions to protect individuals
          and families. We are dedicated to delivering exceptional service and
          helping our clients find the best coverage options tailored to their
          unique needs.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Commitment</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          We understand the importance of having peace of mind when it comes to
          protecting your health and securing your family's future. That's why
          we are committed to offering a wide range of life and health insurance
          products from trusted providers. Our experienced agents work closely
          with you to understand your requirements and guide you through the
          process of selecting the most suitable coverage.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Expertise</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          With years of experience in the insurance industry, our team of
          knowledgeable agents stays up-to-date with the latest trends and
          regulations. We leverage our expertise to ensure that you receive the
          best advice and recommendations for your specific situation. Whether
          you need life insurance to protect your loved ones or health insurance
          to cover medical expenses, we have the knowledge and resources to
          assist you.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Values</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          At AssureGuard Insurance Services, we value integrity, transparency,
          and customer satisfaction above all else. We believe in building
          long-term relationships with our clients based on trust and mutual
          respect. Our goal is to provide you with the support and guidance you
          need to make informed decisions about your insurance coverage.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <a href="/contact-us" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
